    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a vertical uniform rod of length of uppercase L sub R with a pivot located at a distance of lowercase l above the center. A note states that the figure is not drawn to scale.\" src=\"/images/61cf9ac32d7bebaab226014b86d1e736.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A uniform rod of length <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase L sub R\"><math alttext=\"uppercase L sub R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>L</mi><mtext>R</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span> and mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase M sub R\"><math alttext=\"uppercase M sub R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>M</mi><mtext>R</mtext></msub></math></span></span> is free to rotate about a pivot located a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lowercase l\"><math alttext=\"lowercase l\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>ℓ</mo></mstyle></math></span></span>, where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lowercase l is much less than uppercase L sub R\"><math alttext=\"lowercase l is much less than uppercase L sub R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>ℓ</mo><mo>≪</mo><msub><mi>L</mi><mtext>R</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span>, above the rod’s center, as shown in the figure. Which of the following changes could result in a shorter period for small-angle oscillations of the rod? The rotational inertia about the <span class=\"formatted_text text_decoration:underline\">center</span> of the rod is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"one twelfth uppercase M sub R, end sub, uppercase L sub R, end sub, squared\"><math alttext=\"one twelfth uppercase M sub R, end sub, uppercase L sub R, end sub, squared\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>12</mn></mfrac><msub><mi>M</mi><mtext>R</mtext></msub><msup><msub><mi>L</mi><mtext>R</mtext></msub><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span>.</p>\n",
